Builds on material covered in <a href="/search/?P=PA%20541" title="PA&#160;541" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'PA 541');">PA&#160;541</a> and covers more advanced analytical techniques using social science data including count regression models, regression discontinuity designs, instrumental variables, panel data methods, multilevel models. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): Graduate standing; and PA 541or equivalent or approval of the instructor.<br />
